{"tid":2252502,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"澳洲樞機孌童醜聞｜審訊期間梵蒂岡向澳洲匯$380萬 警查是否涉干預","createTime":"2020-10-21T13:25:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-22T04:13:18.000Z","uid":240362,"like":17,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"83c0c5024b82a6bdc1a7fad87f68e7851ae158c9","tid":2252502,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:25:09.000Z","msg":"澳洲金融犯罪監管機構表示，已將前天主教樞機佩爾（George Pell）就孌童案被起訴期間，梵蒂岡被指匯款70萬澳元（約384萬港元）到澳洲的相關資料轉交警方，意大利傳媒報稱這筆錢或被用來賄賂佩爾案中原告。<br />\n<br />\n意大利傳媒近日報道，佩爾涉性侵兒童案在澳洲審訊期間，佩爾的勁敵、意大利樞機貝丘（Angelo Becciu）匯款70萬澳元到澳洲，以協助佩爾的「敵人」去「收買」案中原告。貝丘的律師否認相關報道，佩爾案中原告則透過律師表示「他對任何據稱由梵蒂岡轉到澳洲的支付款項毫不知情」。<br />\n<br />\n澳洲交易報告與分析中心（AUSTRAC）行政總裁羅茜（Nicole Rose）周二對參議院委員會表示，中心已調查相關指控，並將資料轉交澳洲聯邦警方及維多利亞省警方。<br />\n<br />\n原本掌管梵蒂岡財政、曾是教廷第三號人物的澳洲樞機佩爾，就性侵兩名歌詠團男童入獄服刑13個月後，4月獲澳洲高等法院判處無罪。他的律師10月初表示當局必須對意大利傳媒報道的梵蒂岡匯款進行調查，「如果（報道中）所指控的內容可信，那麼必須確保追蹤所有資金活動」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201021/U4DAL7NDONF5LHAZHK3EOLWVVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201021%2FU4DAL7NDONF5LHAZHK3EOLWVVI%2F&d=z3Qy88JfdbGSADH60DObPY429F%2FWQzM9xP7K%2BddLk1E%3D&h=d7acd887\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2F20201021%2FU4DAL7NDONF5LHAZHK3EOLWVVI%2F&h=ddc0ae57\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/international/20201021/U4DAL7NDONF5LHAZHK3EOLWVVI/</a>"},{"pid":"aedb7dd47eb7133c9a6521d1163d1a8a27f722ef","tid":2252502,"uid":36134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:27:01.000Z","msg":"警告過你唔好奶共<br />\n係要迫美帝出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6f2fdf282ddb67cb83f937f88d4e930806ea21df","tid":2252502,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aedb7dd47eb7133c9a6521d1163d1a8a27f722ef","tid":2252502,"uid":36134,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:27:01.000Z","msg":"警告過你唔好奶共<br />\n係要迫美帝出手<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77e18714639f2d0d5645edc8d63fc12646aa9b73","tid":2252502,"uid":233325,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:35:18.000Z","msg":"教廷不嬲係仆街黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲主教搞𡃁仔都搞左好耐，從來都因為要維護個聲譽唔插手，被人投訴就調職，仲有其他仆街嘢。"},{"pid":"df180fd802e7df8dae8671126138797db64253d2","tid":2252502,"uid":56550,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:35:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4MTmgzP.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4MTmgzP.jpg&h=bac8916a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d2c5ededca9dee4ed081d2dec63e383627ae03e8","tid":2252502,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"77e18714639f2d0d5645edc8d63fc12646aa9b73","tid":2252502,"uid":233325,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:35:18.000Z","msg":"教廷不嬲係仆街黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n啲主教搞𡃁仔都搞左好耐，從來都因為要維護個聲譽唔插手，被人投訴就調職，仲有其他仆街嘢。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-21T13:36:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><